+# Exploration 002 Summary
+
+- Goal:
+  screen the surviving Step-10 tensor-family menu across equivalent packagings
+  and decide whether any candidate still earns admission against the frozen full
+  pairing `I_p^far`.
+- What I tried:
+  read the Step-10 goal, the Step-009 freeze and admission-rule reports, the
+  run-006 selected/judgment/attack packet, the Step-001 Tao-gate pressure memo,
+  the far-field pressure obstruction notes, the obstruction-screening notes, and
+  the step-010 receptionist search log; then reduced the live family menu and
+  screened the remaining family across its documented equivalent packagings.
+- Outcome:
+  succeeded.
+- One key takeaway:
+  the live menu collapses to one endpoint-attached `pressure-Hessian /
+  strain-defect` family with `harmonic-moment cancellation` only as a narrow
+  subquestion, and that line still does not survive the repackaging gate because
+  no packaging on disk yields a smaller effective coefficient on the same full
+  pairing `I_p^far`.
+- Packaging screen result:
+  `none survives`.
+- First honest failure:
+  `repackaging obstruction`.
+- Why:
+  the exact pressure relation is only a representation identity unless it
+  changes the coefficient estimate; the eigenframe/alignment variants collapse
+  into local-geometry or criterion language; the restricted-Euler / defect
+  variants collapse into reduced-model or local-defect language; and the
+  harmonic-moment wording counts only if it returns to a smaller coefficient on
+  the full reconstructed pairing, which no local source shows.
+- Leads worth pursuing:
+  only a different branch framing that directly proves remote-shell
+  harmonic-moment cancellation strong enough to shrink the same full-pairing
+  coefficient, rather than changing tensor packaging.
+- Unexpected findings:
+  the repository record is even narrower than the task hypothesis suggested:
+  `full stretching control` is already endpoint drift here, and alignment,
+  eigenframe, restricted-Euler, and conditional-regularity labels function only
+  as overlap comparators, not as live Step-10 survivors.
+- Computations worth doing later:
+  if another branch earns it, the only meaningful computation would be an
+  explicit remote-shell moment-cancellation estimate that comes back to
+  `|I_p^far| <= C_far,eff(k) 2^{12k/5} U_k^{6/5}` with uniform positive-margin
+  shrinkage of `C_far,eff(k)`.
