+# Exploration 002 Report
+
+## Goal
+
+Screen the main equivalent tensor packagings for the surviving Step-10 family
+menu and decide whether any candidate remains live against the frozen full
+pairing `I_p^far`.
+
+## Method
+
+- Read the Step-10 goal and Step-9 endpoint-freeze materials.
+- Extract the serious surviving family menu after overlap reduction.
+- Compare each live family across documented equivalent tensor packagings.
+- Test whether any packaging yields estimate-level action on the same frozen full
+  pairing, as required by the admission rule.
+
+## Findings Log
+
+### Initialization
+
+- Report skeleton created. Source review in progress.
+
+### Source review completed
