+  It survives only as the narrow subquestion of whether pressure-tensor
+  structure can cancel the affine-and-higher harmonic moments that generate the
+  bad coefficient in the same frozen pairing. Sources:
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-009/RESULTS.md`
