+| `harmonic-moment cancellation` subquestion, not a standalone family | [VERIFIED] affine-and-higher harmonic moments of the full pairing; [VERIFIED] local-plus-harmonic pressure split; [INFERRED] pressure-tensor remote-shell cancellation language | [VERIFIED] constants are already killed; affine-and-higher moments remain live; [VERIFIED] this language counts only if it lowers `C_far,eff(k)` for the full reconstructed `I_p^far` pairing | [VERIFIED] same-scale exterior/harmonic remainder is immediate failure if the full pairing comes back with the old coefficient; [INFERRED] absent an estimate-level shrinkage, the subquestion is only another wording for the same non-coercive obstruction | [INFERRED] reject as standalone; fold into row above |
+
+### 3. What Is Packaging-Independent, And What Is Not
+
+#### Packaging-independent claims
+
+- [VERIFIED] The theorem ledger is fixed on the inherited suitable-weak /
