+# Exploration 002 Report
+
+## Goal
+
+Screen the main equivalent tensor packagings for the surviving Step-10 family
+menu and decide whether any candidate remains live against the frozen full
+pairing `I_p^far`.
+
+## Method
+
+- Read the Step-10 goal and Step-9 endpoint-freeze materials.
+- Extract the serious surviving family menu after overlap reduction.
+- Compare each live family across documented equivalent tensor packagings.
+- Test whether any packaging yields estimate-level action on the same frozen full
+  pairing, as required by the admission rule.
+
+## Findings Log
+
+### Initialization
+
+- Report skeleton created. Source review in progress.
+
+### Source review completed
+
+- [VERIFIED] `step-009` already froze the only live theorem ledger, the exact
+  endpoint object `I_p^far`, the progress currency
+  (smaller effective coefficient on that same full pairing), the positive-margin
+  threshold, and the immediate-failure / Tao admission rules.
+- [VERIFIED] The serious live menu entering this screen is not broad. The local
+  record keeps only one endpoint-attached `pressure-Hessian / strain-defect`
+  family, with `harmonic-moment cancellation` surviving only as its narrow
+  subquestion rather than as an independent family.
+- [VERIFIED] Run-006 planning already records the main equivalent packagings of
+  that family as pressure-Hessian/strain misalignment, eigenvalue-gap or other
+  invariant combinations of `S`, `omega`-to-eigenframe alignment, and a
+  restricted-Euler defect quantity with remainder, all sitting next to the
+  exact pressure tensor identity and the stretching package.
+- [INFERRED] No repository source shows a packaging-independent, estimate-level
+  shrinkage of the frozen full-pairing coefficient on `I_p^far`.
+- [INFERRED] The first honest Step-10 failure is `repackaging obstruction`:
+  once the remaining line is screened across its documented equivalent
+  packagings, its apparent novelty washes out into known representation,
+  local-geometry, reduced-model, or criterion language without a smaller
+  coefficient on the same full pairing.
+
+## Findings
+
+### 1. Surviving Family Menu After Overlap Reduction
+
+- [VERIFIED] The frozen Step-009 ledger admits no new theorem endpoint here.
+  Step 10 inherits only one endpoint-attached mechanism family:
+  `pressure-Hessian / strain-defect`, and even that family stays alive only if
+  it acts on the same full far-field pairing `I_p^far`. Sources:
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-009/RESULTS.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-009/explorations/exploration-001/REPORT.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/library-inbox/step-009-exploration-001-endpoint-menu-freeze.md`
+- [VERIFIED] `harmonic-moment cancellation` is not a separate admitted family.
+  It survives only as the narrow subquestion of whether pressure-tensor
+  structure can cancel the affine-and-higher harmonic moments that generate the
+  bad coefficient in the same frozen pairing. Sources:
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-009/RESULTS.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-009/explorations/exploration-002/REPORT.md`
+  - `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/pressure-tensor-identity-remains-only-a-narrow-testable-possibility.md`
+- [VERIFIED] `full stretching control` does not remain live as a separate
+  family. The local record already demoted it to endpoint drift or bottleneck
+  rhetoric unless it returns to the same frozen `I_p^far` inequality. Sources:
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-009/explorations/exploration-001/REPORT.md`
+- [VERIFIED] Alignment, eigenframe, restricted-Euler, and conditional-regularity
+  labels enter this step as overlap comparators, not as separate survivors.
+  Sources:
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-01.md`
+  - `runtime/logs/codex-patlas-beyond-de-giorgi-step-010-receptionist-search.md`
+
+### 2. Packaging Screen
+
+| family | main equivalent packagings | what survives across packagings | known non-coercive collapse | admit or reject |
+| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
+| `pressure-Hessian / strain-defect` | [VERIFIED] exact pressure tensor identity `partial_i partial_j p = R_i R_j(u_i u_j)`; [VERIFIED] stretching / exact `S`-`nabla^2 p` package; [VERIFIED] pressure-Hessian/strain misalignment; [VERIFIED] eigenvalue-gap or invariant combinations of `S`; [VERIFIED] `omega`-to-eigenframe alignment; [VERIFIED] restricted-Euler defect quantity with explicit remainder; [INFERRED] local-plus-harmonic / moment-cancellation wording for the same remote-shell contribution | [VERIFIED] the frozen endpoint and cash-out rule do: only a smaller effective coefficient on the same full pairing `I_p^far` counts; [INFERRED] the only narrow live content is whether exact pressure-tensor structure could force cancellation of the remote-shell affine-and-higher harmonic moments behind that same coefficient | [VERIFIED] representation identity only if stated merely as the exact pressure relation; [INFERRED] local-geometry-only when phrased as eigenframe, invariant, or alignment language; [INFERRED] reduced-model / restricted-Euler flavor when it closes only on a defect variable with remainder or on a local/self-induced piece; [INFERRED] conditional-regularity restatement if promoted as coherence/alignment criterion; [VERIFIED] none of these documented forms earns a smaller coefficient on the same full pairing | [INFERRED] reject |
+| `harmonic-moment cancellation` subquestion, not a standalone family | [VERIFIED] affine-and-higher harmonic moments of the full pairing; [VERIFIED] local-plus-harmonic pressure split; [INFERRED] pressure-tensor remote-shell cancellation language | [VERIFIED] constants are already killed; affine-and-higher moments remain live; [VERIFIED] this language counts only if it lowers `C_far,eff(k)` for the full reconstructed `I_p^far` pairing | [VERIFIED] same-scale exterior/harmonic remainder is immediate failure if the full pairing comes back with the old coefficient; [INFERRED] absent an estimate-level shrinkage, the subquestion is only another wording for the same non-coercive obstruction | [INFERRED] reject as standalone; fold into row above |
+
+### 3. What Is Packaging-Independent, And What Is Not
+
+#### Packaging-independent claims
+
+- [VERIFIED] The theorem ledger is fixed on the inherited suitable-weak /
+  Leray-Hopf plus LEI, CKN/Lin contradiction line, and the live endpoint object
+  is the full pairing `I_p^far`. Sources:
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-009/RESULTS.md`
+  - `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/exact-surviving-far-field-pairing.md`
+- [VERIFIED] Real progress means a genuinely smaller effective coefficient on
+  that same full pairing after later reconstruction and localization debt,
+  not a gain on a subpiece, a cleaner defect variable, or nicer tensor
+  language. Sources:
+  - `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/real-progress-requires-a-smaller-effective-coefficient.md`
+  - `library/meta/obstruction-screening/demand-estimate-level-action-on-the-live-obstruction.md`
+- [VERIFIED] Constants are already annihilated, but affine-and-higher harmonic
+  moments remain live in the exact far-field pairing. Sources:
+  - `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/constant-harmonic-mode-is-automatically-killed.md`
+  - `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/affine-and-higher-harmonic-modes-survive-as-moments.md`
+- [VERIFIED] Tao sensitivity is only an admission screen; it is not leverage
+  unless the same candidate also lowers the frozen full-pairing coefficient.
+  Sources:
+  - `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/tao-sensitivity-is-only-an-admission-screen-unless-the-full-pairing-coefficient-shrinks.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-009/explorations/exploration-003/REPORT.md`
+
+#### Packaging artifacts
+
+- [VERIFIED] The exact pressure relation by itself is only representation
+  language unless it produces a new coefficient estimate. Sources:
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/library-inbox/step-001-exploration-002-tao-gate-pressure-branch.md`
+  - `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/pressure-tensor-identity-remains-only-a-narrow-testable-possibility.md`
+- [INFERRED] Eigenframe language, eigenvalue-gap invariants, and
+  `omega`-to-eigenframe alignment are packaging artifacts at this gate unless
+  they return to a smaller coefficient on the same `I_p^far` pairing. The
+  run-006 record names them as observable variants inside the same crowded
+  prior-art neighborhood, not as distinct endpoint gains. Sources:
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/selected/chain-01.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md`
+- [INFERRED] Restricted-Euler defect wording is a packaging artifact unless it
+  comes with a faithful bridge back to the full far-field pairing rather than a
+  reduced model or local defect variable. Sources:
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/selected/chain-01.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN.md`
+  - `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/same-scale-exterior-or-harmonic-remainder-is-immediate-failure-on-the-full-pairing.md`
+- [INFERRED] Alignment or coherence language is a packaging artifact here if it
+  merely restates known conditional-regularity or local-geometry criteria.
+  Sources:
+  - `library/factual/geometry-route-screening/direction-regularity-is-prior-art-not-a-standalone-novelty-claim.md`
+  - `library/factual/geometry-route-screening/standalone-beltrami-alignment-collapses-to-a-fragility-screen.md`
+  - `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/algebraic-rewrites-and-local-geometry-fail-the-tao-gate.md`
+
+### 4. Where The Candidate Collapses
+
+- [VERIFIED] `representation identity only`:
+  the exact pressure tensor formula remains live only as a narrow testable
+  possibility; as long as it is just `partial_i partial_j p = R_i R_j(u_i u_j)`
+  or another Calderon-Zygmund repackaging, it stays Tao-compatible and does not
+  rescue the branch.
+- [INFERRED] `local geometry only`:
+  once the same line is expressed via eigenframe alignment, invariant
+  combinations of `S`, or local alignment language, the surviving content is
+  only local geometry. That does not directly control the remote-shell moments
+  fixing the coefficient of `I_p^far`.
+- [INFERRED] `reduced-model / restricted-Euler flavor`:
+  once the line is expressed as a defect variable with remainder or any closure
+  that acts only on a local or self-induced part, it hits the frozen kill rule
+  against reduced models that leave the same full pairing untouched.
+- [INFERRED] `conditional-regularity restatement`:
+  if the line is recast as alignment or coherence sufficient for regularity, it
+  becomes the same kind of criterion language the local record already treats
+  as prior art rather than a new endpoint-attached gain.
+
+### 5. Admission Decision
+
+- [VERIFIED] No source in the local repository exhibits a packaging-independent
+  estimate-level gain on the frozen full pairing `I_p^far`.
+- [INFERRED] The only surviving family therefore does not clear Step 10. Its
+  narrow remaining content is a testable question, not an admitted mechanism:
+  whether exact pressure-tensor structure could force remote-shell
+  harmonic-moment cancellation strongly enough to lower the same coefficient.
+- [ADMISSION] `none survives`
+- [INFERRED] First honest failure: `repackaging obstruction`.
+  The family dies as soon as equivalent packagings are screened, because every
+  documented wording collapses into known non-coercive representation,
+  local-geometry, reduced-model, or criterion language before any smaller
+  coefficient on the same full pairing appears.
+- [VERDICT] `repackaging obstruction, branch should stop before tensor-package freeze`
+
+## Dead Ends / Failed Attempts
+
+- [VERIFIED] I searched the local Step-009 freeze materials for a second serious
+  Step-10 survivor beyond `pressure-Hessian / strain-defect` and did not find
+  one. The record repeatedly narrows the live menu back to that one family plus
+  its harmonic-moment subquestion.
+- [VERIFIED] I searched the required local packet for any already-documented
+  estimate on `I_p^far` that remained smaller after switching among the listed
+  tensor packagings. No such packaging-independent coefficient reduction is
+  recorded on disk.
+- [INFERRED] That absence is not merely missing exposition. It is exactly what
+  the run-006 critiques and the Step-009 admission rules warned would kill the
+  branch at the repackaging gate.
+
+## Open Questions
+
+- None within this exploration's scope. The only honest next question would
+  belong to a different branch framing:
+  can one actually prove remote-shell harmonic-moment cancellation strong
+  enough to reduce the same full-pairing coefficient? Step 10 does not earn
+  that continuation on present evidence.
+
